      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out this absolute gem. I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to be thrilled! This car is in truly pristine, mint condition\u2014it honestly looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for that 'brand new' experience without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you. Shoot me a message if you want to come see it!",
      "price": 44900.0,
