    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system for a 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically optimized with documented rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox shifts with clinical precision, paired with a variable M-differential lock for superior lateral traction. The chassis retains its factory-spec damping via an unmolested suspension setup, and the exterior maintains its original luster with zero paint correction required. A peerless specimen for the collector who demands mechanical perfection and historical authenticity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
