    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterpiece of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in breathtaking, showroom-floor condition, meticulously maintained by a single enthusiast owner and stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior features the original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; you will find zero stone chips, scratches, or door dings. The alloy wheels are free of any curb rash and are wrapped in brand-new, period-correct performance tires. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine state, with the premium leather upholstery showing no signs of creasing or bolster wear, and the original floor mats are spotless. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the heated seats, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive, folder-documented service history from the local dealership, including a preventative major service and fluid flush performed just 200 miles ago. This is an investment-grade example for the collector who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
